                <note rend="inline" type="source">693.002/629: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-05-03T18:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 3, 1938—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>138. Your 231, May 3, 11 a.m. The Department approves the reply made by you to
                    the Counselor of the British Embassy. Please repeat to Tokyo through
                    Shanghai.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
